  "A gas at 25°C and 1 atm occupies 5 L. At 75°C and 2 atm, what is its volume?": "",
  "T₁=298K, T₂=348K: (1×5)/298 = (2×V₂)/348; V₂ = (5×348)/(298×2) = 1740/596 ≈ 2.92 L.": ""
